WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
JOHN: Welcome to today's championship match between the Eagles and the Hawks!

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:07.200
MIKE: The Eagles are looking strong in the first quarter with their aggressive offense.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:11.800
JOHN: Johnson takes the shot from the three-point line... and it's good! Eagles lead 15-12.

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:15.400
SARAH: The Hawks are responding well with their defensive strategy.

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:19.100
MIKE: Smith drives to the basket, avoids the block, and scores! What a play!

00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:23.600
JOHN: Timeout called by the Eagles coach. They need to regroup after that last possession.

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:27.300
SARAH: The crowd is electric tonight! Over 15,000 fans in attendance.

00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:31.000
MIKE: Back from the timeout, the Eagles inbound the ball to Thompson.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:34.700
JOHN: Thompson passes to Williams who's open in the corner...

00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:38.400
SARAH: Williams shoots! It's off the rim but Davis gets the rebound!

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:42.100
MIKE: Davis with the putback! That's his second basket of the quarter.

00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:45.800
JOHN: The Hawks are calling for a timeout. They need to stop this Eagles run.

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:49.500
SARAH: We're seeing some great basketball here tonight. Both teams are giving it their all.

00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:53.200
MIKE: The Eagles have been dominant in the paint tonight, outscoring the Hawks 20-12.

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:56.900
JOHN: And here comes the Hawks' star player, Martinez, looking to make an impact.

00:00:56.900 --> 00:01:00.600
SARAH: Martinez with a beautiful crossover move! He's got the defender on skates!

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:04.300
MIKE: Martinez pulls up for the three... and it's nothing but net! Hawks cut the lead to 2.

00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:08.000
JOHN: What a response from Martinez! The Hawks are back in this game.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:11.700
SARAH: The energy in the arena has completely shifted. The Hawks fans are on their feet!

00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:15.400
MIKE: Eagles inbound the ball quickly, looking to maintain their momentum.

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:19.100
JOHN: Johnson receives the pass and immediately looks for the open man.

00:01:19.100 --> 00:01:22.800
SARAH: Williams is cutting to the basket! Johnson threads the needle with a perfect pass.

00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:26.500
MIKE: Williams goes up strong! He's fouled on the shot attempt.

00:01:26.500 --> 00:01:30.200
JOHN: Williams will go to the free throw line for two shots. This could be crucial.

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:33.900
SARAH: Williams steps to the line, takes a deep breath, and sinks the first free throw.

00:01:33.900 --> 00:01:37.600
MIKE: And he makes the second one as well! Eagles extend their lead back to 4.

00:01:37.600 --> 00:01:41.300
JOHN: The Hawks need to respond quickly. Time is running out in this quarter.

00:01:41.300 --> 00:01:45.000
SARAH: Martinez brings the ball up court, looking to create something for his team.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.700
MIKE: Martinez drives hard to the basket! He's going to try to draw the foul.

00:01:48.700 --> 00:01:52.400
JOHN: Martinez goes up for the layup... and he's fouled! He'll go to the line.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:56.100
SARAH: This is exactly what the Hawks needed. Martinez has been their go-to player.

00:01:56.100 --> 00:02:00.000
MIKE: Martinez makes both free throws! The Hawks are now within 2 points again.
